 CBNuGrid args;id;eventName;logMsg;currentLog;row;col;mouseFlag
‚çù NuGrid event callback handler
‚çù Logs events to the F1.Log label
‚çù args is flattened: id eventName info[1] info[2] info[3] ...

 id‚Üê‚äÉargs
 eventName‚Üê2‚äÉargs

‚çù Format the event message based on event type
 :Select eventName
 :Case 'CellMove'
     ‚çù Info: [row, col, scrollFlag, selectionFlag, mouseFlag, changedFlag, newValue]
     row‚Üê3‚äÉargs
     col‚Üê4‚äÉargs
     mouseFlag‚Üê7‚äÉargs
     logMsg‚Üê'CellMove: Row ',(‚çïrow),' Col ',(‚çïcol),(mouseFlag=0)/' (kbd)'
     logMsg,‚Üê(mouseFlag=1)/' (click)'
 :Case 'KeyPress'
     ‚çù Info: [key, charCode, keyCode, shiftState]
     logMsg‚Üê'KeyPress: "',(‚çï3‚äÉargs),'" shift=',‚çï6‚äÉargs
 :CaseList 'MouseDown' 'MouseUp' 'MouseDblClick'
     ‚çù Info: [y, x, button, shiftState]
     logMsg‚ÜêeventName,': Y=',(‚çï3‚äÉargs),' X=',(‚çï4‚äÉargs),' Btn=',‚çï5‚äÉargs
 :Case 'MouseEnter'
     logMsg‚Üê'MouseEnter'
 :Case 'MouseLeave'
     logMsg‚Üê'MouseLeave'
 :Else
     logMsg‚ÜêeventName,': ',‚çï2‚Üìargs
 :EndSelect

‚çù Update the event log label (prepend new event)
 currentLog‚Üê'F1.Log'eWG'Caption'
 'F1.Log'eWS'Caption'(logMsg,(‚éïUCS 10),currentLog)
